      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal test sample characterisation not required at MRL 2 beyond documented test conditions.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterisation (batch-to-batch blood variability) not required at MRL 2. Hematocrit and viscosity measured per batch; values within protocol specification. Factor assessed as not-assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
