      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2; qualitative assessment of parameter alignment between validation and COU is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative review confirms that validation experiment input parameters (fluid properties, operating conditions, geometry) are equivalent to COU parameters within acceptable bounds. Formal quantitative equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2 and not performed."
